  <h2>API Authentication</h2>
  <p>To access your app's resources you need to create a unique
  signature for each request, as follows:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <code>X-Access-Token</code>: A pre-shared access token.
    </li>
    <li>
      <code>X-Access-Timestamp</code>: The current time UNIX UTC
    timestamp as an integer. Requests are valid for 1 minute, to
    prevent replay attacks.
    </li>
    <li>
      <code>X-Request-Hash</code>: A HMAC hexdigest hash of the
      following elements concatenated:
      <ul>
        <li>
          SHA1 hash
        </li>
        <li>
          Pre-shared secret key (unique for each access token).
        </li>
        <li>
          Request data: HTPP Verb + UNIX UTC timestamp + Query
        params
        </li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>

