    <li>Verb: <code>POST</code></li>
    <li>Secret: <code>11ba566229f0d670bc4e650168e2f2ad</code></li>
    <li>Request parameters:
      <ul class="task-list">
        <li><code>key0 = value0</code></li>
        <li><code>key1 = value1</code></li>
      </ul>
    </li>
    <li>Timestamp: <code>1384178851</code></li>
  </ul>

  <p>Final hash function input: <code>POST11ba566229f0d670bc4e650168e2f2adkey0=value0&amp;key1=value11384178851</code></p>

  <p>The example input would result in the following request hash: <code>66f3845e935f15366f098e2ca912566799316a2d</code></p>

  <p>So the final request would look something like this:</p>

  <pre>
    <code>POST /users?key0=value0&amp;key1=value1 HTTP/1.1
    ...
    X-Access-Token: 31cb1c0f1c885b7421731f0cc225aabd
    X-Request-Timestamp: 1384178851
    X-Request-Hash: muaAxT1J6pqwMmMaDfQFPZrVFLZqR8AiuXfxb88D+V4=
  </code></pre>

  <p>If a request fails to validate, the server will respond with <code>401 Unauthorized</code>.</p>

